edu.ucla.sspace.util
Class SetDecorator<T>

java.lang.Object
  edu.ucla.sspace.util.SetDecorator<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, Set<T>
public class SetDecorator<T>
extends Object
implements Set<T>, Serializable

A wrapper around an existing Set implementation that allows classes to extend the functionality of a set by overriding some of its methods. For example, a subclass could enforce a size capacity on an existing set by overriding add and addAll to not add elements beyond a certain number.
